spec_data.Name: python3-breathe
spec_data.Description:
Breathe is an extension to reStructuredText and Sphinx to be able to read and
render the Doxygen xml output.
spec_data.Signature: RSA/SHA256, Tue 22 Aug 2017 10:28:17 AM EDT, Key ID f55e7430f5282ee4
spec_data.Summary: Adds support for Doxygen xml output to reStructuredText and Sphinx
